<center><table border=0><tr><td><center><H2><font face=arial>This is true and leads to a good idea on Zone importance...(TXT read)</font></H2></center>
<font face=arial size=2><b>Posted By:</b> <A HREF="/cgi-local/whois2.cgi?Kellindel">Kellindel</a><br>
<b>Posted On:</b> 1:17 p.m. 9/2/1999<br>
<b>Subject:</b> This is true and leads to a good idea on Zone importance...(TXT read)<p>
<br><center><img src="http://www.everworld.net/pvpquest/images/divider.gif" width=452 height=22 border=0></center><BR><P ALIGN=CENTER><b>In Reply To:</b> <A HREF="http://www.everworld.net/cgi-local/pvp.cgi?read=316" TARGET=_self>Hmm... (txt)</A> (Raeus)
</STRONG><FONT SIZE=2 color=#FFFFFF FACE=arial>
<P>Its obvious with such a diverse game like EQ... there should be racial hatred in the game.

<BR>Whatever the reason is...
<BR>For instance.. a wood elf ranger should be able to kill Ogres and Trolls and maybe even Dark elves with out any restrctions.
<BR>In this case the ranger would have to travel into the Ogre and Troll territory to accomplish such feats.. and when there he will be at a disadvantage and can get jumped by numerous npcs as well as PCs.
<BR>This wil make a great roleplaying side of EQ... and thus giving Zones and areas of the map some importance and influence on where u travel...
<BR>Likewise.. if an Ogre thinks he can go to Fadywar and bash some heads in... he could do that by hunting the roads and forests for would be easy kills... tho could run into a band of elves or whatever and get serously jacked up.
<BR>I can see this situatuion easily.. a PC Ogre Warrior is terroszing the inhabitants of Fadywar and its up to some of the locals to beat them down.. and kick thier sorry hides off their land.
<P>
</FONT></td></tr></table></P>
